{"nodes": [{"id": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cortex_temporal_hive_mind_atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_md", "label": "RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "source_location": "L1", "content": "---\ntags: [atom, resolver, skill-dispatch]\nstatus: active\ncreated: 2026-05-30\nupdated: 2026-05-30\n---\n\n# RESOLVER \u2014 Skill Dispatcher\n\nInspirado no GBrain do Garry Tan. Mapeia triggers \u2192 skills. O agente l\u00ea antes de agir.\n\n## Thinking Skills (GStack-inspired)\n\n| Trigger | A\u00e7\u00e3o |\n|---------|------|\n| \"Brainstorm\", \"tenho uma ideia\" | 6 forcing questions |\n| \"Review esse plano\", \"CEO review\" | Desafiar premissas, 4 modos de escopo |\n| \"Debug\", \"corrigir\", \"quebrado\" | Investiga\u00e7\u00e3o sistem\u00e1tica, no fixes without investigation |\n| \"Retro\", \"o que shipamos\" | Weekly retro com per-person breakdowns |\n\n## Always-On\n\n- Toda mensagem \u2192 carregar current-state + brain-first\n- Toda decis\u00e3o de build \u2192 Boil the Lake, Search Before Building\n- Qualquer decis\u00e3o registrada \u2192 salvar com frontmatter YAML\n- Qualquer aprendizado \u2192 salvar com tags apropriadas\n\n## Regras de Desambigua\u00e7\u00e3o\n\n1. Prefira a mais espec\u00edfica\n2. Se menciona pessoa/empresa/projeto \u2192 pasta espec\u00edfica\n3. Se menciona URL \u2192 identificar tipo e rotear\n\nLinks: [[Key Decisions]], [[Current State]]\n"}, {"id": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_resolver_skill_dispatcher", "label": "RESOLVER \u2014 Skill Dispatcher", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "source_location": "L8"}, {"id": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_thinking_skills_gstack_inspired", "label": "Thinking Skills (GStack-inspired)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "source_location": "L12"}, {"id": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_always_on", "label": "Always-On", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "source_location": "L21"}, {"id": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_regras_de_desambigua\u00e7\u00e3o", "label": "Regras de Desambigua\u00e7\u00e3o", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "source_location": "L28"}], "edges": [{"source": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cortex_temporal_hive_mind_atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_md", "target": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_resolver_skill_dispatcher", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "source_location": "L8", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_resolver_skill_dispatcher", "target": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_thinking_skills_gstack_inspired", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "source_location": "L12", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_resolver_skill_dispatcher", "target": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_always_on", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "source_location": "L21", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_resolver_skill_dispatcher", "target": "atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_regras_de_desambigua\u00e7\u00e3o", "relation": "contains", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "source_file": "cortex/temporal/Hive-Mind/atoms/RESOLVER-Skill-Dispatcher.md", "source_location": "L28", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cortex_temporal_hive_mind_atoms_resolver_skill_dispatcher_md", "target": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cortex_temporal_h